    src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_46598252-ff89-4700-80f2-2e535177697e_brazilian-waxing-scottsdale.jpg"
    alt="Brazilian wax service at Rejuvenate You in Scottsdale"
    class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover rounded-xl"
  />
</div>

<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  Remove all unwanted hair with our premium Brazilian wax service at Rejuvenate You. Experience minimal pain and discomfort. Book a consultation today!
</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Benefits of a Brazilian Wax in Scottsdale</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_493ba91d-a9ae-41e2-aa68-dd58b7715b00_benefits-of-brazilian-waxing.jpg"
      alt="Benefits of Brazilian waxing"
      class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="mb-4">
      Opting for our full Brazilian wax service in Scottsdale offers many advantages. Consider the negative aspects of shaving. When you shave, the hair can grow thicker, itchier, and coarser. The shaving process doesn't provide a long-term solution either.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
      <li>Longer-lasting results than shaving</li>
